{"tid":1698850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10.20 紀錄片: 一路上","createTime":"2019-11-07T19:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T19:51:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4536721444d6f00c5679987ab3fb6b6dd592e2de","tid":1698850,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:41:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N1swoLP1Os4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN1swoLP1Os4&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=e8cd78c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N1swoLP1Os4</a><br />\n<br />\n【10.20 一路上】<br />\n<br />\n片長：22分鐘<br />\n<br />\n10月20日民陣發起九龍大遊行，獲「反對通知書」，市民自發上街，尖沙咀、旺角人頭湧湧。早前民陣召集人岑子杰遇襲，懷疑兇徒南亞裔人士，有港人自發到重慶大廈、清真寺作保護。警方下午4時開始清場，出動水炮車，「銳武」裝甲車裝甲車清除障礙物，沿路「無差別」發射水炮，警民關係進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n記者：關震海、陳卓斯、王紀堯、公民記者張倫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【☂➡️支持《誌》請 follow #誌 #hk.feature⬅️🌕】<br />\n👋誌IG ➣ <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/feature_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffeature_hk%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=bafa915a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/feature_hk/</a><br />\n👋Youtube channel➣ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ytrbpd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ytrbpd&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=f06a136f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ytrbpd</a><br />\n👋 Medium ➣ <a href=\"https://medium.com/feature-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Ffeature-hk&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=b16736af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/feature-hk</a><br />\n👋 Telegram➣ <a href=\"https://t.me/HK_feature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_feature&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=ae8d2954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt